OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777821065
OL,3,CFormer Tory councillor who drugged and
OL,4,Craped wife admits indecent images
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FA former Swindon councillor who
OL,8,Fpreviously admitted drugging and
OL,9,Fraping his now ex-wife has pleaded
OL,10,Fguilty to possessing indecent images
OL,11,Fof children.
OL,13,FFormer Tory councillor Philip Young,
OL,14,F49, appeared before Winchester Crown
OL,15,FCourt on Friday morning.
OL,17,FDuring a hearing at the court in
OL,18,FJanuary, he entered guilty pleas to
OL,19,Foffences including rape, sexual
OL,20,Fassault, assault by penetration and
OL,21,Fvoyeurism.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
