FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777821065
OL,3,CFormer Tory councillor who drugged and
OL,4,Craped wife admits indecent images
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FHe pleaded guilty to a further eight
OL,8,Fcharges on Friday, including three
OL,9,Fcharges of making indecent images of
OL,10,Fchildren and one of possessing
OL,11,Fprohibited images of children in July
OL,12,F2024.
OL,14,FThe defendant, who appeared via video
OL,15,Flink from prison, also admitted four
OL,16,Fcounts of possessing an extreme
OL,17,Fpornographic image between January
OL,18,F2019 and January 2024.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
