PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777821065
OL,3,CFormer Tory councillor who drugged and
OL,4,Craped wife admits indecent images
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FJudge Paul Dugdale told the court that
OL,8,FYoung's pleas to all 56 charges
OL,9,Fagainst him meant he would not stand
OL,10,Ftrial.
OL,12,FYoung published more than 500 intimate
OL,13,Fimages and videos of his ex-wife
OL,14,Fwithout her consent between 2010 and
OL,15,F2024.
OL,17,FFive other men have previously
OL,18,Fappeared in court charged with sexual
OL,19,Foffences against Mrs Young.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
