PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777821065
OL,3,CFormer Tory councillor who drugged and
OL,4,Craped wife admits indecent images
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FDean Hamilton, 47, of no fixed abode,
OL,8,Fhas admitted one charge of assault by
OL,9,Fpenetration, two of sexual assault and
OL,10,Fone of rape.
OL,12,FNorman Macksoni, 48, of Wood End Close
OL,13,Fin Sharnbrook, Bedfordshire, has
OL,14,Fdenied one count of rape and one of
OL,15,Fpossessing an extreme pornographic
OL,16,Fimage.
OL,18,FRichard Wilkins, 61, of Toothill,
OL,19,FSwindon, Wiltshire, has denied one
OL,20,Fcount of rape and one of assault by
OL,21,Fpenetration.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
