PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1777821065
OL,3,CFormer Tory councillor who drugged and
OL,4,Craped wife admits indecent images
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FConnor Sanderson-Doyle, 31, of Crofton
OL,8,FRoad, Swindon, has denied sexual
OL,9,Fassault by penetration and sexual
OL,10,Fassault.
OL,12,FMohammed Hassan, 37, of Torun Way in
OL,13,FSwindon, has denied sexual touching.
OL,15,FMacksoni, Wilkins, Sanderson-Doyle and
OL,16,FHassan are due to stand trial on
OL,17,FOctober 5.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
